chmod owner-group-world file OR directory
i.e => chmod 775 fouad.php

1 -> executable
4 -> Read
2 -> Write

---------------------
chown ==> this command to change the owner and group of file OR directory

chown  owner:group FILE OR DIRECTORY

i.e  (chown root:tom fouad.php) ==> this change the owner of the file to root and the group to tom
i.e  (chown :tom)               ==> this will change only the group-owner to tom and leave the default for owner
